seharusnya mati justru tidak.

00:20:20.160 --> 00:20:21.160
Naruto!

00:20:22.000 --> 00:20:23.600
Apakah kau mau memaafkan mereka?

00:20:24.800 --> 00:20:26.700
<i>Maafkan aku, Sasuke.</i>

00:20:37.700 --> 00:20:39.860
Sungguh ironis.

00:20:40.300 --> 00:20:42.210
Pertentangan ini ...

00:20:42.210 --> 00:20:44.260
